verse = \lyricmode {
  The earth, which you have foun -- ded, none can shake.
The ra -- ging deep you as its cloak did make,
and e -- ven moun -- tains were con -- cealed there -- un -- der;
the wa -- ters fled at your re -- buke, your thun -- der.
They down the hills their way to val -- leys found;
the migh -- ty wa -- ters you with li -- mits bound.
So you as -- signed their place to them, that nev -- er
their roar -- ing floods the earth a -- gain might cov -- er.
}
